GRANT

Dear @lanawintersvny Happy Birthday, not sure how many years you’ve been 26 now, but who’s counting. 
You’re fiery, intelligent, stunning and paid me to write this post obviously. 
You discovered me. You brought me to NY 18 years ago, and had to learn rather quickly I was an absolute tornado. I was your ring boy, your dad was my chaperone abroad for years (even though it didn’t help) until he retired from that responsibility, I was the first to know about your babies and have raised me as your child since day one. Apologies @nicolastomczakwinters and @chloetwinters (the real children) 
 It’s impossible to put into words to others how much you’ve changed my life, but you have. Everything I have today is a greater part directly because of you. You’re an incredible mother, manager, matcha drinker, dog mom but above all else, human. I love you to pieces La. Here’s to another 18 together by your side

Now back to my 2/3 word posts
